&lt;p&gt;Nymbus is building the next generation of fintech platforms and that requires a new kind of product builder. This role is the engine of the squad — the person who takes product intent and turns it into working software. You will design, specify, and build products using AI-first methodology, working hand-in-hand with your Architect and Shipper to deliver outcomes end-to-end.&lt;/p&gt;
