&lt;p&gt;This is not a traditional developer or product owner role. You are a full-stack product builder who authors specifications, writes code, designs interactions, and iterates rapidly using AI-assisted workflows. You own the &quot;what&quot; and the &quot;how&quot; — translating domain problems into working, shippable software.&lt;/p&gt;
