&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect (Your Partner):&lt;/strong&gt; Owns system design, technical integrity, and cross-squad consistency. The Architect ensures your solutions are scalable, maintainable, and aligned with platform architecture. You collaborate daily on data models, API contracts, and integration patterns.&lt;/p&gt;
