&lt;li&gt;Hold SLA accountability; ensure client commitments are met consistently and predictably across the book of business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and develop two established operational leaders and their teams; set performance expectations and optimize the layer of management beneath them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the senior escalation point for operational client issues requiring executive-level engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
